description:
Implement endpoint to check generation job status.

## Endpoint: GET /api/status/{job_id}

## Response Schema
```json
{
  "job_id": "uuid-string",
  "status": "processing",           // pending|processing|completed|failed
  "progress": 50,                    // 0-100 percentage
  "message": "Generating variants...",
  "created_at": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "completed_at": null,
  "error": null,
  "result": null                     // populated when completed
}
```

## Result Schema (when completed)
```json
{
  "result": {
    "output_dir": "cat-20240101-120000",
    "variants": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "original": "/api/files/cat-20240101-120000/originals/variant-1.png",
        "processed": {
          "1024": "/api/files/.../processed/variant-1/AppIcon-1024.png",
          "180": "/api/files/.../processed/variant-1/AppIcon-180.png"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

## Files to Modify/Create
- `src/icon_generator/api/routes/status.py`
- `src/icon_generator/api/schemas.py` (add StatusResponse)

## Dependencies
- ios-app-icons-dh6 (FastAPI setup)
- ios-app-icons-9ye (Job queue)
